S tozi kod mojem da convertirame mejdu kilogrami i paundove.

Formulata e slednata:

Ako iskame ot kilogrami kum paundove, umnojavame s 2.2


Ako puk iskame obratnoto, shte razdelim na 2.2

###

enter_kg_or_lbs = input("Enter what measure\nyou want to convert(kg or lbs): ")
enter_number = float(input("Enter amount to convert: "))

if enter_kg_or_lbs == "kg":

    converted_amount = enter_number * 2.2
    print(f"{enter_number:.2f} kilograms is {converted_amount:.2f} pounds.")

elif enter_kg_or_lbs == "lbs":

    converted_amount = enter_number / 2.2
    print(f"{enter_number:.2f} pounds is {converted_amount:.2f} kilograms.")

else:

    print("Please choose between KG or LBS.")
